text: Schinznach is a municipality of the district Brugg in the canton of Aargau in Switzerland. On 1 January 2014, the former municipalities of Oberflachs and Schinznach-Dorf merged into the new municipality of Schinznach. ==Gallery== File:Schinznach-Dorf 8527.JPG|Schinzach-Dorf File:Oberflachs 8523.JPG|Oberflachs ==References== ==Other websites== * Official Website Category:Municipalities in Brugg Category:2014 establishments in Switzerland
